ResourceIdentifier.name: ResourceIdentifier
ResourceIdentifier.description: An identifier of the resource parameter pertaining to a notification.

ResourceState.name: ResourceState
ResourceState.description: A selection from a set of state levels used in resource thresholds.

PowerSupplyState.name: PowerSupplyState
PowerSupplyState.description: A selection from a set of state levels used in power supply status.

SnmpVersions.name: SnmpVersions
SnmpVersions.description: An indicator of which SNMP versions are enabled.

EnabledOrNot.name: EnabledOrNot
EnabledOrNot.description: An indication of whether a feature is configured as enabled or disabled.

RemoteAuthType.name: RemoteAuthType
RemoteAuthType.description: An indication of which remote authentication are enabled.

resourceNumberOfFilesystems.name: resourceNumberOfFilesystems
resourceNumberOfFilesystems.description: The number of filesystems on the device's hard disk.

resourceFSEntry.name: resourceFSEntry
resourceFSEntry.description: An entry in the resource filesystem table. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

resourceFSInUseMB.name: resourceFSInUseMB
resourceFSInUseMB.description: The number of MB in use for this filesystem.

resourceFSThresholdMaj.name: resourceFSThresholdMaj
resourceFSThresholdMaj.description: The major threshold value (percent) in use for this filesystem.

resourceFSThresholdCrit.name: resourceFSThresholdCrit
resourceFSThresholdCrit.description: The critical threshold value (percent) in use for this filesystem.

resourceFSRangeMin.name: resourceFSRangeMin
resourceFSRangeMin.description: The minimum value of the range of MB in use (usually zero).

resourceFSRangeMax.name: resourceFSRangeMax
resourceFSRangeMax.description: The size (in MB) of this filesystem.

resourceFSIndex.name: resourceFSIndex
resourceFSIndex.description: The number of this table row, from one to the number of filesystems.

resourceFSEncryption.name: resourceFSEncryption
resourceFSEncryption.description: Indicates whether this filesystem is encrypted or not.

resourceHPMemoryObjs.name: resourceHPMemoryObjs
resourceHPMemoryObjs.description: Sub-tree of host processor memory information.

resourceHPMemoryInUsePercent.name: resourceHPMemoryInUsePercent
resourceHPMemoryInUsePercent.description: The percentage of host processor memory in use.

resourceHPMemoryThresholdMaj.name: resourceHPMemoryThresholdMaj
resourceHPMemoryThresholdMaj.description: The major threshold value for host processor memory in use.

resourceHPMemoryThresholdCrit.name: resourceHPMemoryThresholdCrit
resourceHPMemoryThresholdCrit.description: The critical threshold value for host processor memory in use.

resourceHPMemoryRangeMin.name: resourceHPMemoryRangeMin
resourceHPMemoryRangeMin.description: The minimum percentage of host processor memory in use (usually zero).

resourceHPMemoryRangeMax.name: resourceHPMemoryRangeMax
resourceHPMemoryRangeMax.description: The maximum percentage of host processor memory in use (usually 100).

resourceHPMemoryTotal.name: resourceHPMemoryTotal
resourceHPMemoryTotal.description: The size (in bytes) of host processor memory.

resourceHPCPUObjs.name: resourceHPCPUObjs
resourceHPCPUObjs.description: Sub-tree of host processor CPU information.

resourceHPCPUBusyPercent.name: resourceHPCPUBusyPercent
resourceHPCPUBusyPercent.description: The percentage of host processor CPU busy.

resourceHPCPUThresholdMaj.name: resourceHPCPUThresholdMaj
resourceHPCPUThresholdMaj.description: The major threshold value for host processor CPU busy.

resourceHPCPUThresholdCrit.name: resourceHPCPUThresholdCrit
resourceHPCPUThresholdCrit.description: The critical threshold value for host processor CPU busy.

resourceHPCPURangeMin.name: resourceHPCPURangeMin
resourceHPCPURangeMin.description: The minimum percentage of host processor CPU busy (usually zero).

resourceHPCPURangeMax.name: resourceHPCPURangeMax
resourceHPCPURangeMax.description: The maximum percentage of host processor CPU busy (usually 100).

resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier2A.name: resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier2A
resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier2A.description: F Thread Utilization of XLR A

resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier3A.name: resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier3A
resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier3A.description: KS Thread Utilization of XLR A

resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier4A.name: resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier4A
resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier4A.description: L Thread Utilization of XLR A

resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier2B.name: resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier2B
resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier2B.description: F Thread Utilization of XLR B

resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier3B.name: resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier3B
resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier3B.description: KS Thread Utilization of XLR B

resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier4B.name: resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier4B
resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier4B.description: L Thread Utilization of XLR B

resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier2C.name: resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier2C
resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier2C.description: F Thread Utilization of XLR C

resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier3C.name: resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier3C
resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier3C.description: KS Thread Utilization of XLR C

resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier4C.name: resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier4C
resourceNPCPUBusyPercentTier4C.description: L Thread Utilization of XLR C

resourceChassisTempDegreesC.name: resourceChassisTempDegreesC
resourceChassisTempDegreesC.description: The chassis temperature in degrees C.

resourceChassisTempThresholdMaj.name: resourceChassisTempThresholdMaj
resourceChassisTempThresholdMaj.description: The major threshold value for chassis temperature.

resourceChassisTempThresholdCrit.name: resourceChassisTempThresholdCrit
resourceChassisTempThresholdCrit.description: The critical threshold value for chassis temperature.

resourceChassisTempRangeMin.name: resourceChassisTempRangeMin
resourceChassisTempRangeMin.description: The minimum value of the chassis temperature range.

resourceChassisTempRangeMax.name: resourceChassisTempRangeMax
resourceChassisTempRangeMax.description: The maximum value of the chassis temperature range.

resourcePowerSupplyStatus.name: resourcePowerSupplyStatus
resourcePowerSupplyStatus.description: DEPRECATED as of TOS V. 3.5.0. If the device has dual power supplies and power supply monitoring is enabled, this value indicates whether one or both power supplies is functional (red or green respectively). Otherwise the value is unknown.

resourcePowerSupplyQuantity.name: resourcePowerSupplyQuantity
resourcePowerSupplyQuantity.description: The number of power supplies (1 or 2).

resourcePowerSupplyMonitoring.name: resourcePowerSupplyMonitoring
resourcePowerSupplyMonitoring.description: If power supply monitoring is currently enabled, this value is 1; otherwise, this value is 0.

resourcePowerSupplyTable.name: resourcePowerSupplyTable
resourcePowerSupplyTable.description: Table of power supplies on the device. The number of entries depends on the value of resourcePowerSupplyQuantity. The maximum number of entries is implementation dependent.

resourcePowerSupplyEntry.name: resourcePowerSupplyEntry
resourcePowerSupplyEntry.description: An entry in the power supply table. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

powerSupplyUnitIndex.name: powerSupplyUnitIndex
powerSupplyUnitIndex.description: Index into the power supply units on a device. Starts with 1

powerSupplyStatus.name: powerSupplyStatus
powerSupplyStatus.description: If the device has dual power supplies and power supply monitoring is enabled, this value indicates whether one or both power supplies is functional (red or green respectively). Otherwise the value is unknown.

resourceLogCountObjs.name: resourceLogCountObjs
resourceLogCountObjs.description: Sub-tree of system log entry counts by type.

resourceLogCountCritical.name: resourceLogCountCritical
resourceLogCountCritical.description: The number of system log entries of type 'critical'.

resourceLogCountError.name: resourceLogCountError
resourceLogCountError.description: The number of system log entries of type 'error'.

resourceLogCountWarning.name: resourceLogCountWarning
resourceLogCountWarning.description: The number of system log entries of type 'warning'.

resourceLogCountInfo.name: resourceLogCountInfo
resourceLogCountInfo.description: The number of system log entries of type 'info'.

resourceMetricObjs.name: resourceMetricObjs
resourceMetricObjs.description: Sub-tree of selected system performance metrics.

resourceMetricFastpath.name: resourceMetricFastpath
resourceMetricFastpath.description: Fast path throughput in bits per second.

resourceMetricSmartpath.name: resourceMetricSmartpath
resourceMetricSmartpath.description: Smart path throughput in bits per second.

resourceDateTime.name: resourceDateTime
resourceDateTime.description: Current date and time of device in seconds since January 1, 1970. No timezone offset (UTC)

resourceSnmpRunState.name: resourceSnmpRunState
resourceSnmpRunState.description: An indicator of which SNMP versions are running on the device.

resourceSnmpConfig.name: resourceSnmpConfig
resourceSnmpConfig.description: An indicator of which SNMP versions are configured on the device.

resourceRemoteAuthEnabled.name: resourceRemoteAuthEnabled
resourceRemoteAuthEnabled.description: An indicator of whether remote authentication is enabled on the device.

resourceRemoteAuthTimeout.name: resourceRemoteAuthTimeout
resourceRemoteAuthTimeout.description: The configured remote authentication timeout value in seconds.

resourceRemoteAuthType.name: resourceRemoteAuthType
resourceRemoteAuthType.description: An indicator of which remote authentication mechanism is enabled on the device.

tptResourceNotifyDeviceID.name: tptResourceNotifyDeviceID
tptResourceNotifyDeviceID.description: The unique identifier of the device sending this notification.

tptResourceNotifyIdentifier.name: tptResourceNotifyIdentifier
tptResourceNotifyIdentifier.description: The type of the resource that triggered this notification.

tptResourceNotifyFSIndex.name: tptResourceNotifyFSIndex
tptResourceNotifyFSIndex.description: For a filesystem resource, the index of the filesystem (otherwise 0).

tptResourceNotifyCurrentValue.name: tptResourceNotifyCurrentValue
tptResourceNotifyCurrentValue.description: The current value of the resource that triggered this notification.

tptResourceNotifyThresholdMaj.name: tptResourceNotifyThresholdMaj
tptResourceNotifyThresholdMaj.description: The major threshold of this resource (between green and yellow states).

tptResourceNotifyThresholdCrit.name: tptResourceNotifyThresholdCrit
tptResourceNotifyThresholdCrit.description: The critical threshold of this resource (between yellow and red states).

tptResourceNotifyRangeMin.name: tptResourceNotifyRangeMin
tptResourceNotifyRangeMin.description: The minimum end of the range of values that this resource can take.

tptResourceNotifyRangeMax.name: tptResourceNotifyRangeMax
tptResourceNotifyRangeMax.description: The maximum end of the range of values that this resource can take.

tptResourceNotifyStateBefore.name: tptResourceNotifyStateBefore
tptResourceNotifyStateBefore.description: The state of this resource before the current threshold transition.

tptResourceNotifyStateAfter.name: tptResourceNotifyStateAfter
tptResourceNotifyStateAfter.description: The state of this resource after the current threshold transition.

tptResourceNotifyTimeStamp.name: tptResourceNotifyTimeStamp
tptResourceNotifyTimeStamp.description: The time of the threshold crossing represented by this notification (in seconds since January 1, 1970).

tptResourceNotifySubIdentifier.name: tptResourceNotifySubIdentifier
tptResourceNotifySubIdentifier.description: Sub-Identifier into the type of the resource which trigger this notification. It starts with 1. It is not used in models 5100N or older (set to 0).

tptResourceNotify.name: tptResourceNotify
tptResourceNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that a resource parameter has crossed a predefined threshold.
